OOC: Meteara's at the North Pole, no tlikely to just happen up there and 
notice her, especially since she's with Firaxis.

::Firaxis::
       He nods solemnly at Meteara, "Then we should go quickly."  He 
transforms into his bird mode and Horn transforms into his rocket sled mode 
and they fly towards the battle.
